social_posts.post_text: The Clausen’s throw one hell of a party. Thanks for having me DJ 🙏🏻🥳 @jessclausen @jimmyclausen

What. A. Night! Feeling so grateful to be surrounded by such an amazing group of people. You guys make this party what it is every single year! A night full of endless laughs, the best energy and nothing but insane fun. And thank you to my amazing hubby @jimmyclausen and the whole crew for always making me feel special on my birthday even though this is a Holiday party🤣. Can’t wait until next year, rest up everyone

I know you’re tired of these pics, and it takes me an eternity to get a post up…but I just love these people so much - the people who fill our cup! We are so lucky to be surrounded by so much love…our crew who we parent with, do allll the kids sports and activities with, and also have the BEST time with when we get a break. Nothing but good vibes and energy with this group, and for that we are so damn lucky! (Missed a few of our favorites this year, but we will make up for it next year!!)

Also…this party was planned, then cancelled, and then brought back 5 days before it was supposed to happen and everyone was still down even after making all their outfit returns and changing their plans. We love you guys so much, and promise not to take you on the roller coaster ride again next year! 😂

Thank you for all the birthday love too. I appreciate you all more than you know✨🤍💛
Oh look…there’s more! Turns out when you’re sent over 800 photos, it’s hard to just choose a few!! Love our people so much and don’t know what we’d do without you all🫶🏻
Merry Christmas from our fam to yours! Beyond grateful🖤
My wild girl…you are everything and more!!
Making these memories with my babies makes it all worth it🖤And the last video needs to be here permanently. #speeduptoslowdown
